Czech Koruna Weakens for Second Day, Slides 0.2% Against Euro

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-02-21T08:30:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/czech-koruna-weakens-for-second-day-slides-0-2-against-euro.html
The Czech koruna slid for a second
day, weakening 0.2 percent to 24.483 per euro as of 9:10 a.m. in
Prague.  To contact the reporter on this story:
